ese\nadjacent regimes -- without reference to linearization. The\n$L^\\alpha$-Kantorovich-Rubinstein distance $d_\\alpha$ which quantifies\nstability is chosen to match the attraction exponent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 25 Jul 2021 03:31:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 May 2022 14:50:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-19"}
